-MWirWLX1cX1weamp_EP.text: The suspect's vehicle and the stolen vehicle were last seen heading southbound on Snelling Avenue. The suspect's vehicle is reported to be a black Buick Rendezvous occupied by three men and a woman.

-MWivXkh1xYpl4LzEDFH.text: The vehicle was last seen on N 47th Ave & N Colfax Ave.
